snippet.title: Moto Racer 1 (1997) ALL TRACKS in HD | Championship
snippet.description:
This video will run through all the tracks in Moto Racer. 
► Want to watch individual tracks? Open the description! 
The gamemode is "Championship" and the difficulty is "Medium".

The video includes all the tracks from both the "Plugin Data Disk" and the "TwoNewIslands Data Disk". 

The tracks that are featured in the video: 
0:51 - Speed Bay
4:01 - Snow Ride
6:52 - West Way
9:41 - Dirt Arena
13:02 - Rock Forest
15:59 - Lost Ruins
19:42 - Red City 
22:53 - Great Wall
27:06 - Fun Fair
31:13 - Sea of Sand

Want to buy the game yourself? Head over to http://www.gog.com/gamecard/moto_racer and buy it for only $3!
